Purpose

Define a standardized process for escalating unresolved issues to Tier 2 or Engineering.

Scope

Applies to all Tier 1 support agents.

Process

Confirm all standard troubleshooting steps have been completed

Gather customer environment details (device, connection type, error messages)

Document the issue clearly in the ticket

Assign escalation with appropriate priority level

Notify relevant team if urgent

Expected Outcome

Reduce unnecessary escalations

Improve resolution time

Ensure clear communication between teams
